{"tid":1021980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門輕鐵攔腰撞巴士 輕鐵服務受阻","createTime":"2019-02-14T15:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T15:38:29.000Z","uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a1d463ea3f1dfade68da957772ed8dfa2455659c","tid":1021980,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T15:35:24.000Z","msg":"屯門輕鐵攔腰撞巴士 輕鐵服務受阻<br />\n最後更新: 0214 23:15 /\t建立時間 (HKT): 0214 23:05<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190214/large/1550157404_9b1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190214%2Flarge%2F1550157404_9b1f.jpg&h=42c50677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴士車身及輕鐵車頭嚴重損毀。(網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n晚上10時許，一輛由深圳灣口岸前往屯門碼頭的B3城巴士，駛至輕鐵兆麟站附近時，遭一輛507綫輕鐵列車攔腰撞及。巴士車身及輕鐵車頭嚴重損毀，505、507及614綫輕鐵的服務受阻，警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190214/59261023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190214%2F59261023&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=cd9c57dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190214%2F59261023&h=56a9e06f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190214/59261023</a>"},{"pid":"9527b09e562fedf83805f08ecc5f4c5b0b6554b4","tid":1021980,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T15:36:35.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"0e119b65f42cab6ac9abd39624dcc346719990c1","tid":1021980,"uid":52276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"撞死啲支那水貨狗就啱！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}